  "description": "The temporary erection and installation of circa 75no wooden cabins across the London Bridge City estate for the Christmas Market Event from 5th November 2021 - 8th January (inclusive of load in and load out). There will be 7 Zones of cabins across the estate and along Queen's Walk including; Zone 1 - Riverside/Scoop, Zone 2 - Riverside/Strada Steps, Zone 3 - Riverside/HMS Belfast, Zone 4 - Riverside/Upper Deck bar (by HMS Belfast), Zone 5 -\rRiverside/Southwark Crown Court, Zone 6 - Hay's Galleria and Zone 7 - London Bridge City Pier. There will also be a screen installed at London Bridge City Pier. The cabins will measure 10x8ft, 10x6ft, 10x5ft, 10x4ft and 20x10ft, respectively. There will be a range of Hot and Cold beverages/food, Arts & Crafts and general goods themes. This will include a large bar to the top of The Scoop, Riverside. The bar will be created by overlapping two 20ft customised insulated hi-top shipping containers as well as wooden cabins to provide additional seating and a decked outdoor area themed as an Alpine styled Apr?s bar. Total footprint is 24m x 9m. This area will include all bar storage, lighting/sound control and office area. Exteriors and back of house will be clad and sealed with attractive panels/hoarding as per the wider event theme.",
